<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<main class="flex-1 pt-24 pb-20 px-6 transition-colors duration-500 
    bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 via-blue-200 to-blue-300 
    dark:bg-gradient-to-r dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-black">

  <!-- Privacy Policy Section -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 
                bg-white/80 dark:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl 
                border border-blue-200 dark:border-white/20 overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-500">

      <!-- Gradient Overlay for Light Mode -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-200/40 to-indigo-300/40 dark:hidden pointer-events-none rounded-2xl"></div>
      <!-- Dark-mode Tint Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 hidden dark:block bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/10 to-purple-700/10 pointer-events-none rounded-2xl"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-black dark:text-white mb-6 text-center drop-shadow">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          At the <span class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-indigo-300">MITS Placement Predictor Portal</span>, 
          we value and respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-indigo-300 mt-6 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We collect personal details such as name, email address, academic records (CGPA, SSC marks, etc.), and 
          self-assessed skill data. This information is used solely for generating skill ratings and placement predictions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-indigo-300 mt-6 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          The data provided by you is used to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Generate personalized skill ratings and placement predictions.</li>
          <li>Provide insights to students and faculty for career preparation.</li>
          <li>Improve the accuracy of our machine learning models.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-indigo-300 mt-6 mb-3">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We implement strict security protocols to protect your information from unauthorized access, modification, or misuse. 
          Your data is encrypted and stored securely.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-indigo-300 mt-6 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We do not share or sell your personal data to third parties. Your data is used exclusively for academic and 
          placement-related predictions at MITS.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-indigo-300 mt-6 mb-3">5. Your Consent</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          By using this portal, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-6 text-center">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact the MITS administration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

